{"tid":1031492,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[字海] ASMR意境流第二階段，覺醒!","createTime":"2019-02-21T16:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T13:08:56.000Z","uid":28823,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ce31b73196ccf213e419db44573f640946f40f","tid":1031492,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"2年前比鴨清叫我去聽ASMR，但我9個月前開始聽入迷日日聽，依家個腦覺醒左一樣野...<br />\n就係我聽ASMR除左大腦麻痺，賓周仔已經開始唔識扯旗，我就知道我進入左下一個領域....<br />\n其實都唔想講咁多野，好累....去片!!!<br />\n<br />\n0:00 - 0:16秒，魔物處男既神情，大家睇完，有咩咩感受?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P0M2aoUEn2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP0M2aoUEn2s&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=c42fb7a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P0M2aoUEn2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00 - 0:20秒，教主係俄羅斯跑到仆街望上天見到極光，大家睇完，有咩咩感受?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfPKGubnA7Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRfPKGubnA7Y&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=1e2b5130\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfPKGubnA7Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗯，視角同聽覺既合併，可以產生到無限可能性，我見有一種意境走入腦，係意境流!<br />\nASMR係帶來好多好處，最有效係令人解壓，但過程實在太長..<br />\n但當你進行第二段領域，你會發覺短短幾秒就可以令你解壓同大腦放鬆，就好似依兩段片...<br />\n<br />\n9個月前，我要每日凌晏12點開始聽1個鐘ASMR先可以解到壓訓教面對明天工作!!!<br />\n依家，我只需要短短20秒(loop 5次以上)，3分鐘內就可以上到狀態.....<br />\n<br />\n可能好多人有唔同方法令自己內心寧靜，佛教念經，耶教唱詩，但......唔講了"},{"pid":"8766255ccbc42fa8f89f4cd9da174bf21b49ee71","tid":1031492,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗拍拖咩,咁得閒上黎發神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa50339d929097b1676ac40f111443c14a91454b","tid":1031492,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e79313b9a915535c7